## Citation rules

- Every `proposed_body` you produce MUST cite the source via a
  wikilink to `{{ source_vault_path }}`.
- Use `match_existing` when a proposed name equals an existing name
  or any of its aliases; `action` becomes `extend` in that case.
- Do not add claims not present in the source.

Ultrathink about whether each extracted name semantically matches an
existing vault name or alias before proposing `create`. Near-misses
(capitalization, pluralization, abbreviation, common alias) must
resolve to `match_existing` + `action: extend`, not `create`.

Return status DONE with the workdir path when every builder call
has returned ok.
